snippet.title: Engaging Young Children in the Outdoor Environment  (Video #166)
snippet.description: Outdoor environments are more than swing sets and slides! This Apples Video Magazine will address the Illinois Early Learning Standards in revealing the mysterious process of creating an outdoor classroom. Young children can be equally engaged in learning through play outdoors as they are indoors. Viewers will understand the value of play in outdoor settings that promote social interactions, independence, creativity, and most importantly, friendships. Join the fun as we view outdoor play. Recorded: September 2009

snippet.title: Indoor Playground Business (How to Start?)
snippet.description:
How to start an Indoor Playground Business in 8 EASY STEPS TO FOLLOW:
or Visit our Website at www.asiaparksdvt.com

1. Find your target location for business (Must have high foot traffic, family recreation areas like malls, supermarkets, parks)
2. Submit you letter of intent to lease
3. Contact us for ocular inspection, playground design and conceptualization and costing.
4. Sign Contracts (Contract of Lease with Lessor and Supply / Construction contract with US)
5. Submit business requirements to lessor (store facade design, layouts and plans) and local government (business permit application, BIR registration, Construction Plans if needed)
6. Conduct Pre-Marketing for awareness (with our assistance)
7. Operate Business
8. COUNT YOUR EARNINGS!

snippet.title: Bumper Jumpers Indoor Playground, Indoor Birthday Parties and Rentals
snippet.description:
Bumper Jumpers Indoor Playground is Greensboro NC and The Triad areas number one Indoor Playground, Party Venue, and Inflatable Rental location around! Each of our locations are temperature-controlled, filled with amazing inflatables, games, and other activities to ensure learning through creative play, regardless of the weather outside. In addition, all play areas at Bumper Jumpers are shoe-free. We are proud to be a place where parents can relax and watch their children play and have fun or even join in! That’s Right, Parents can jump and play too!

Bumper Jumper’s is the most exciting , adventurous, and enjoyable birthday party location in Greensboro; our birthday party venue is full of bouncing, sliding, jumping fun for your child and all your birthday party guests, we even provide you with child’s birthday music! We  offer wall-to-wall inflatables, a variety of arcade games, full concession options and a dedicated party room, with your own private hostess that can provide you if need with fun and amazing birthday party ideas, so you can sit back, relax, and enjoy your child’s special day and let us at Bumper Jumpers do all the set-up and clean-up.

Our facilities offer a variety of birthday packages for your child and their guests. We also offer the option to rent the top of the line inflatables to bring the party to you! From the mechanical bull, to the wipe out, we can cover any party or event inflatable need!

Socks are required for both kids and adults so that everyone leaves as clean as they arrive! If you have no socks, BJ’s has souvenir Bumper Jumpers Socks available for purchase. As the safety of your children is of utmost importance to us, Bumper Jumpers takes pride in its safety and security measures. We maintain a strict policy that each child must be accompanied by an adult; and too, we closely monitor the flow of traffic in and out of each facility through our computerized tracking systems, backed by the diligence of our staff. Our facilities are equipped with surveillance camera recording at all times.

 www.bumperjumpers.com

snippet.title: McDonald's Indoor Playground Playtime. Happy Meal and Family Fun with Chase and Cole Adventures
snippet.description:
McDonald's Indoor Playground Playtime. Happy Meal and Family Fun with Chase and Cole Adventures. Thank you for watching our Family Channel!

With the rainy weather taking over Memorial Day we had to call an audible. Fortunately, we have a McDonalds playground a few miles down the road from our house, so we took our Holiday Adventure to Ronald's house and his indoor playground. An afternoon of slides, climbs, obstacle courses, and of course, Happy Meals, was just what the doctored ordered. 

The Happy Meal prizes are original board games from my childhood so we have enjoyed the prize surprises just as much as the boys these past few weeks. Connect4 is still my favorite but who doesn't like BattleShip and Operation? Hopefully the weather clears up next weekend so we can take our Adventures to the beach, but we will never complain about an afternoon at McDonalds 😋😛

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE YOUTUBE KIDS VIDEOS 😀

https://bit.ly/2DID85td

Welcome to our family channel, Chase and Cole Adventures, where Chase and Cole want to be your friends so they can help make your day a fun-filled adventure. If you're looking for entertaining, safe and family friendly content then subscribe now and have your family Join the Adventure!
 
We really want to provide you with videos your family will enjoy watching, so we go beyond unboxing toys and doing the traditional toy review videos, by taking you, and the cool toys, on their very own Adventure. Whether it's trips to Amusement Parks, the beach, a fun game of tag, gameplay of our favorite video games, pretend play or one of our awesome rescue missions, Chase and Cole want to bring you on their Adventures and have you experience all the fun that's possible with the latest new toys.
 
We will be posting NEW videos to our kids channel every Thursday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday.
